<div id="zh-question-title" data-editable="false">

<h2 class="zm-item-title zm-editable-content">

<a href="/question/29337260">有哪些经典的战前动员讲话？</a>

</h2>
</div>
<div id="zh-question-detail" class="zm-item-rich-text" data-resourceid="3917770" data-action="/question/detail">

<div class="zm-editable-content">人类历史发生了诸多的战争斗争，有为保卫家国，有为民族气节，有为道德理想，请问各位大神有没有读过经典的战前动员讲话？</div>


</div>
